First of all, make sure that your local django, mysqld, apache and blabla works well
Change the configuration in neupCMS_config.py.sample to localize the website
and rename it as neupCMS_config.py
Put the UEeditor directory in neupCMS/media/editor/ueditor
Then run 'python neupCMS/manage.py syncdb'
Now,It should be running 囧

The 'www.neupioneer.com' branch is developed for the need of our website
new useful feature of the branch will be merged to the master

